---
description: MotionGuard repository engineering and governance rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `AGENTS.md` and the active Linear issue before changing code. Keep `@motionguard/core`
browser-agnostic. Use strict TypeScript and deterministic tests. Treat inspected pages as untrusted.
Run `pnpm qa` after meaningful changes. Do not merge, publish, deploy, or perform destructive actions
without the required gate and explicit authority. Visual assets must follow the repository's
1920×1080 quality standard.
